ttps://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02183120/Esker-Ride-Scholarship-bike-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Anyone can apply between now and the end of July, telling Esker, “why they think they would be a good fit for the ride scholarship, and what they plan to do with a new Esker hardtail mountain bike”. They say they’re especially encouraging newer riders with a vision, but they really just want to get the ball rolling and help out someone with a passion for mountain biking, adventure, and storytelling.</p><p>Up for grabs is either a complete <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/09/12/hayduke-lives-esker-cycles-re-releases-steel-hardtail-w-lighter-frame-new-geo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hayduke</a> or <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/11/24/esker-cycles-seeks-hardtail-zen-with-modern-steel-japhy-featuring-room-for-29-x-2-8-tires/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Japhy</a> in the size and color of your choice, for you to expand your mountain biking horizons, and spread the good word. More details and application at: <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/ride-scholarship\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EskerCycles.com</a></p><h3><span>more le (<em>alt</em>) Tour&nbsp;</span></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/u