ent/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174324/Lachlan-Morton-EF-Alt-Tour-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><ul><li><strong>Lachlan’s Alt Tour already raises 208,000€&nbsp;for World Bicycle Relief</strong> – We kinda can’t get over how crazy and a little stupid Lachlan Morton’s own self-supported bikepacking <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/28/lachlan-morton-to-ride-all-21-stages-of-tour-de-france-plus-transfers-in-his-alt-tour/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alt Tour</a> de France is. Inspired by the inaugural 1903 TdF, he’s trying to ride every stage and every transfer of the Tour before the peloton, covering a distance of 5,500km and climbing over 65,000 meters in just 23 days. And he’s doing it to raise money to support World Bicycle Relief. Riding in sandals on flat pedals to combat some knee pain, he’s already knocked back 2000km, more than 22,000m of climbing, and raised over two hundred thousand euros. Follow along at: <a href=\"https://alttour.ef.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AltTour.EF.com</a></li></ul><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BqsGXpNyiD8?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><ul><li>Ride your own L’Étape du Tour, in the Czech Republic this time – Sure, Lachlan is riding all the stages in France, but why not try a Tour stage hidden a bit further east in the Czech lands? The regular French L’Étape du Tour where you ride one of the actual race stages couldn’t happen this year because of ongoing COVID restrictions, but the one in Prague is still going ahead. L’Etape Czech Republic by le Tour de France run Aug 28, 2021 from Prague and around Central Bohemia is not just a 130km amateur race, but also a family festival day too. Find out more and register at: <a href=\"https://www.letapeczech.cz/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LEtapeCzech.cz</a></li></ul><p><span>Gear &amp; Deals</span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/02174330/L39ION-of-LA-Rapha-kit-Cait-Oppermann_team-riding-700x420.jpg 700